2003-04-10	Adrian Perez	<mobius@iespana.es>
	* defs.h: added strdup() replacement.
	* shelve.c: metatable used in the 'shelf' userdata is no longer
			stored in the namespace table of the module, it's in the Lua
			registry instead.

2003-04-08	Adrian Perez	<mobius@iespana.es>
	* shelve.c: added '__tostring' metamethod to the 'shelf' userdata,
			the returned string contains file name and read-write mode info.
	* shelve.c: fixed some bugs derived from popping string values from
			the stack before using them.
	* shelve.c: fixed small memory leak (I forgot a free() in the '__gc' 
			metamethod).
	* ChangeLog: ChangeLog started.

